			<a href="/"><button>The Latest</button></a>
		</div>
		<div class="cell grid-x latest-story-container">
											<div class="cell auto tertiary-story">
					<div class="story-img-container">
						<a href="https://lithub.com/inside-the-inferno-revisiting-southern-californias-first-wildfire-of-2025/" title="Inside the Inferno: Revisiting Southern California’s First Wildfire of 2025"><img class="story-img" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/12/wildfire-300x300.jpg"></a>
					</div>
					<div class="story-content-container">
						<h2><a href="https://lithub.com/inside-the-inferno-revisiting-southern-californias-first-wildfire-of-2025/" title="Inside the Inferno: Revisiting Southern California’s First Wildfire of 2025">Inside the Inferno: Revisiting Southern California’s First Wildfire of 2025</a></h2>
					</div>
				</div>
